{"tid":1299922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［選舉前］將麗芸一句說話值得2000正評？","createTime":"2019-07-09T08:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T09:21:59.000Z","uid":232575,"like":150,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f04f6cace97c77c24c6332ee8fd3568a78050459","tid":1299922,"uid":232575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:05:01.000Z","msg":"我明白依2000正評係唔代票2000票。<br />\n但中間派會因為依2000正評而覺得將麗芸有支持度。<br />\n可能有人會因為依句說話既「正面輿論」而覺得民建聯「開明」（作噁）。<br />\n<br />\n選舉前必須槍口對外，唔好再畀語言藝術呃到。<br />\n<br />\n無論佢地話咩「人話」，都唔可以以「正面輿論」回應"},{"pid":"bf70cff164b3bfb8adb4e036bc6daee13733cc90","tid":1299922,"uid":212626,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:07:51.000Z","msg":"元秋講嘢不嬲冇邏輯 唔用腦<br />\n話唔定佢聽日又打倒今日的我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507f8abe236ff13781fd3b87f2370a8bc3ab26d9","tid":1299922,"uid":212182,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:08:24.000Z","msg":"其實大家心知狗改不了吃屎"},{"pid":"eee5fb49b03b159545157424a275f6e6aabe6930","tid":1299922,"uid":52524,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:08:50.000Z","msg":"正評當睇小丑"},{"pid":"930b3aa164b67c36718b12c8a2a0f9d50b8a2155","tid":1299922,"uid":65582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"蔣麗<del>人云亦</del>芸"},{"pid":"152141f862a5e5f03673b1d9cb140bba4206ab97","tid":1299922,"uid":8175,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:09:23.000Z","msg":"條友只不過為左選舉先講返句人話<br />\n選完肯定又變返癲婆"},{"pid":"1a0aa6be8bc9054f495d4a614c33e795ac61fc22","tid":1299922,"uid":174752,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:10:04.000Z","msg":"你暗串泛民議員？<br />\n<br />\n叫人唔好因為佢哋最近做過既應有其事，而忘記佢哋 過往二十幾年點樣出賣香港人？<br />\n<br />\n分化撚"},{"pid":"151e5b1b8fdb9c719a988edc27fd0a07c3e26666","tid":1299922,"uid":117251,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:10:18.000Z","msg":"當笑話聽<br />\n覺得好笑所以正評<br />\n目標趕走建制出議會"},{"pid":"f6820de9a50ab4cb00da04cfa0bf91e7239c87af","tid":1299922,"uid":160605,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bohOcyS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbohOcyS.png&h=ba84312e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02d5c83f7e95cbb8c01e61220f7c1ee191eb09e5","tid":1299922,"uid":83309,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:12:51.000Z","msg":"動機係咩都好 起碼元秋佢講得出 <br />\n好過開記者會排隊企出黎宜家冇晒影果堆<br />\n<br />\n正評亦都反映連登唔係為反而反 仍然有理性"},{"pid":"f9046d23a807d333eea4647e3a3bf1f4bad6e6ae","tid":1299922,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:13:52.000Z","msg":"歡迎入內討論<br />\n<br />\n「長文慎入」勇武又好、和理非又好，自己香港自己救！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1299934/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1299934/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"466fa7696e24097caf5005dc84597bcfe3adde8a","tid":1299922,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:14:09.000Z","msg":"正評唔洗錢  不過笑完就算"},{"pid":"2a32555190722cd86d9b2a32d0dfd8926b329f8d","tid":1299922,"uid":153418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f6820de9a50ab4cb00da04cfa0bf91e7239c87af","tid":1299922,"uid":160605,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bohOcyS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbohOcyS.png&h=ba84312e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />nice job"},{"pid":"b43dc247f513693c2eb3fa5dca46d65ae1ffd86f","tid":1299922,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"但係佢嗰句說話亦都提醒左中立派<br />\n林鄭根本冇回應過任何訴求"},{"pid":"99b664b2a37b1f9a2f68fb4ff9b29b8b37602ab9","tid":1299922,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"